      "content": "hey im having a nightmare with my globaltech cloud instance. its throwing a 504 gateway timeout on every single request but only when i try to call the specific oauth endpoint for the legacy database connector. i checked my subnet settings and they seem fine, and there's no downtime reported in the status dashboard. i've tried restarting the container and checking the logs but it just keeps timing out without a specific error message in the app logs. can u fix this asap?? im losing money every hour this is down.",
